'''波士頓'''（{{lang-en|Boston}}）為[[美國|美國]][[麻省|麻省]]{{link-en|联邦 (美國州)|Commonwealth (U.S. state)|联邦}}[[首府|首府]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Population and Housing Occupancy Status: 2010 – State – County Subdivision 2010 Census Redistricting Data (Public Law 94-171) Summary File|url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST16&prodType=table|publisher=[[United_States_Census_Bureau|United States Census Bureau]]|year=2010|accessdate=2013-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141020164959/http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST16&prodType=table|archive-date=2014-10-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>，佔地面積{{convert|48.4|mi2|0}}<ref>{{Cite web|title=Boston by the Numbers: Land Area and Use|url=http://www.bostonplans.org/getattachment/86dd4b02-a7f3-499e-874e-53b7e8be4770#:~:text=%E2%80%94%20With%20a%20land%20area%20of,up%20the%20Commonwealth%20of%20Massachusetts.|access-date=2022-03-28|author=Boston Redevelopment Authority|date=2018-08-25|format=pdf|language=en}}</ref>，2018年居民總數為694,583人，是麻省乃至[[新英倫|新英倫]]地區{{link-en|麻省市政區列表|List of municipalities in Massachusetts|人口最多的城市}}<ref name="2010census"/><ref name="USCensusEst2018">{{cite web|url=https://www.census.gov/programs-surveys/popest/data/tables.2018.html|title=Population and Housing Unit Estimates|accessdate=2019-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170529192346/https://census.gov/programs-surveys/popest/data/tables.2016.html|archive-date=2017-05-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也是[[按人口排列的美國城市列表|全美第24大城市]]。其為[[大波士顿|大波士頓]]（[[大都市統計區|大都市統計區]]）的經濟與文化中心，並於1999年7月1日前，為[[沙福克縣_(麻省)|沙福克縣]]縣政府的代表議席<ref>{{cite web|title=List of intact or abandoned Massachusetts county governments|url=https://www.sec.state.ma.us/cis/cisctlist/ctlistcounin.htm|website=sec.state.ma.us|publisher=Secretary of the Commonwealth of Massachusetts|accessdate=2016-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190326211309/http://www.sec.state.ma.us/cis/cisctlist/ctlistcounin.htm|archive-date=2019-03-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年的人口普查结果顯示，以波士頓領銜的大波士頓擁有480萬人口，乃全美第十大的大都會區<ref name=BostonMetroPopulation>{{cite web|url=https://factfinder.census.gov/bkmk/table/1.0/en/PEP/2016/PEPANNRES/310M300US14460|title=Annual Estimates of the Resident Population: April 1, 2010 to July 1, 2016 Population Estimates|publisher=[[United_States_Census_Bureau|United States Census Bureau]]|accessdate=2017-06-03|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200213114755/https://factfinder.census.gov/bkmk/table/1.0/en/PEP/2016/PEPANNRES/310M300US14460|archive-date=2020-02-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>；以波士頓為中心的{{link-en|廣域都市統計區|Combined statistical area}}則擁有820萬人口，乃全美第六大<ref>{{cite web|url=https://factfinder.census.gov/bkmk/table/1.0/en/PEP/2016/PEPANNRES/330M300US148|title=Annual Estimates of the Resident Population: April 1, 2010 to July 1, 2016 Population Estimates Boston-Worcester-Providence, MA-RI-NH-CT CSA|publisher=United States Census Bureau|accessdate=2017-06-03|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200213085551/https://factfinder.census.gov/bkmk/table/1.0/en/PEP/2016/PEPANNRES/330M300US148|archive-date=2020-02-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

波士頓為美國最古老的都市之一，於1630年由遷移美洲的[[清教徒|清教徒]]在{{link-en|邵馬特半島|Shawmut Peninsula}}上建立。<ref name="history">{{cite web |last=Banner |first=David |title=Boston History – The History of Boston, Massachusetts |url=http://www.searchboston.com/articles/history.html |publisher=SearchBoston |accessdate=2009-04-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090315031352/http://www.searchboston.com/articles/history.html |archivedate=2009-03-15  }}</ref>{{sfn|Kennedy|1994|pp=11–12}}[[美國獨立戰爭|美國獨立戰爭]]前夕及期间，多場重要事件均发生于此，如[[波士頓大屠殺|波士頓大屠殺]]、[[波士頓傾茶事件|波士頓傾茶事件]]、[[邦克山戰役|邦克山戰役]]及[[波士顿之围|波士頓之圍]]等。美国脱离[[大不列顛王國|大不列顛王國]]獨立後，波士頓繼續作為其不可或缺的港口、製造業基地以及教育文化中心。<ref name=AboutBoston>{{cite web|url=http://www.cityofboston.gov/visitors/about.asp|title=About Boston|publisher=City of Boston|accessdate=2016-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100527093243/http://www.cityofboston.gov/visitors/about.asp|archive-date=2010-05-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>{{sfn|Morris|2005|p=8}}該市後來以填海及市區吞併的形式擴張土地，範圍不再規限於半島本身。波士顿深厚的歷史底蕴吸引不少旅客慕名而來，仅[[法尼尔厅|法尼爾廳]]每年便有2千萬人次到訪。<ref name="BostonTourism">{{cite web|url=http://www.thetravelerszone.com/travel-destinations/top-25-most-visited-tourist-destinations-in-america/|title=Top 25 Most Visited Tourist Destinations in America|date=2008-05-10|publisher=The Travelers Zone|accessdate=2013-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190410082122/http://www.thetravelerszone.com/travel-destinations/top-25-most-visited-tourist-destinations-in-america/|archive-date=2019-04-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>波士頓於美國創下诸多领域之先河，包括全美首個公眾公園（1634年成立的[[波士顿公园|波士頓公園]]）、首間公立或州立學校（1635年成立的[[波士顿拉丁学校|波士頓拉丁學校]]）及首個地鐵系統（1897年建立的{{link-en|特莱蒙街地鐵|Tremont Street subway}}）。<ref name="BPS">{{cite web |url=http://www.boston.k12.ma.us/bps/bpsglance.asp#students |title=BPS at a Glance |publisher=Boston Public Schools |date=2007-03-14|accessdate=2007-04-28| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070403011648/http://boston.k12.ma.us/bps/bpsglance.asp| archivedate=2007-04-03}}</ref>

今日的波士頓急速發展。{{link-en|波士頓都會區大專院校列表|List of colleges and universities in metropolitan Boston|其多所著名的學府}}使之成為國際[[高等教育|高等教育]]中心<ref>{{Cite web|title=World Reputation Rankings|url=https://www.timeshighereducation.com/world-university-rankings/2016/reputation-ranking|access-date=2022-03-28|date=2016-04-21|work=Times Higher Education|language=en}}</ref>，為醫學、工程、法律、商學重鎮，並為全球[[創新|創新]]及[[創業|創業]]先鋒，具有近5,000家[[初创企业|初創企業]]。<ref name=VentureCapitalBoston1>{{cite web|url=http://nvca.org/research/venture-investment/|title=Venture Investment – Regional Aggregate Data|publisher=National Venture Capital Association and PricewaterhouseCoopers|accessdate=2016-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408104240/http://nvca.org/research/venture-investment/|archive-date=2016-04-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Kirsner">{{cite news|url=http://www.boston.com/business/technology/innoeco/2010/07/boston_is_1but_will_we_hold_on.html|title=Boston is #1 ... But will we hold on to the top spot? – Innovation Economy|work=The Boston Globe|date=2010-07-20|accessdate=2010-08-30|first=Scott|last=Kirsner|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304222353/http://www.boston.com/business/technology/innoeco/2010/07/boston_is_1but_will_we_hold_on.html|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite report |title= Innovation that Matters 2016 |publisher= US Chamber of Commerce |url= http://www.1776.vc/reports/innovation-that-matters-2016/ |date= 2016 |access-date= 2019-09-06 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190906155531/https://www.1776.vc/reports/innovation-that-matters-2016/ |archive-date= 2019-09-06 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>波士頓的經濟發展亦建基於[[金融|金融]]、專業商業服務、[[生物技術|生物技術]]、[[信息技术|信息技術]]及政治活動。<ref name=BostonFinance>[https://www.longfinance.net/media/documents/GFCI_24_final_Report_7kGxEKS.pdf] {{Wayback|url=https://www.longfinance.net/media/documents/GFCI_24_final_Report_7kGxEKS.pdf |date=20190805061330 }} Accessed October 7, 2018.</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bostonredevelopmentauthority.org/PDF/ResearchPublications/TheBostonEconomyin2010.pdf | title=The Boston Economy in 2010 | publisher=Boston Redevelopment Authority | date=January 2011 | accessdate=2013-03-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120730182721/http://www.bostonredevelopmentauthority.org/PDF/ResearchPublications//TheBostonEconomyin2010.pdf |archivedate=2012-07-30}}</ref>當地居民之平均[[博愛精神|博愛精神]]獲評為全美最高<ref name="transfer of wealth">{{cite web| url=http://www.tbf.org/~/media/TBFOrg/Files/Reports/Wealth%20Transfer%20Report%202013.pdf| title=Transfer of Wealth in Boston| publisher=The Boston Foundation| date=March 2013| accessdate=2015-12-06| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190412072452/https://www.tbf.org/~/media/TBFOrg/Files/Reports/Wealth| archive-date=2019-04-12| dead-url=yes}}</ref>；商業機構之環境[[可持续发展|可持續發展]]投資亦領銜全國<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.cityofboston.gov/news/Default.aspx?id=6332| title=Boston Ranked Most Energy-Efficient City in the United States| publisher=City Government of Boston| date=2013-09-18| accessdate=2015-12-06| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330070518/https://www.cityofboston.gov/news/Default.aspx?id=6332| archive-date=2019-03-30| dead-url=yes}}</ref>。波士頓曾經歷[[士紳化|士紳化]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://boston.curbed.com/2016/12/7/13867040/which-boston-neighborhoods-will-gentrify|title=Which Boston neighborhoods will gentrify next?|author=Tom Acitelli|publisher=Vox Media|date=2016-12-07|accessdate=2016-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330070523/https://boston.curbed.com/2016/12/7/13867040/which-boston-neighborhoods-will-gentrify|archive-date=2019-03-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，現在的[[生活成本|生活成本]]在全美最高之列<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.sfgate.com/ontheblock/2016/12/10/in-the-wake-of-the-ghost-ship-fire-examining-oaklands-staggering-rent-hikes/#photo-781392|title=In the wake of the Ghost Ship fire, examining Oakland's 'staggering' rent hikes|date=2016-12-10|accessdate=2016-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330055117/https://blog.sfgate.com/ontheblock/2016/12/10/in-the-wake-of-the-ghost-ship-fire-examining-oaklands-staggering-rent-hikes/#photo-781392|archive-date=2019-03-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Heudorfer">{{cite web |author1=Heudorfer, Bonnie |author2=Bluestone, Barry |url=http://www.tbf.org/uploadedFiles/Housing%20Report%20Card%202004.pdf |title=The Greater Boston Housing Report Card |publisher=Center for Urban and Regional Policy (CURP), Northeastern University |page=6 |accessdate=2016-12-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061108003526/http://www.tbf.org/uploadedFiles/Housing%20Report%20Card%202004.pdf |archivedate=2006-11-08  }}</ref>，但仍獲評為全球最宜居的地方之一<ref name="quality of living">{{cite web| url=http://www.mercer.com/referencecontent.htm?idContent=1173105 | title = Quality of Living global city rankings 2010 – Mercer survey | publisher=[[Mercer_(consulting_firm)|Mercer]]| date=2010-05-26| accessdate=2011-08-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110812003533/http://www.mercer.com/referencecontent.htm?idContent=1173105 |archivedate=2011-08-12}}</ref>。

== 历史 ==
